code: @Test public void testGetAgeIsReadOnly() throws Exception {     ModelMBeanInfo info = getMBeanInfoFromAssembler().     ModelMBeanAttributeInfo attr = info.getAttribute(AGE_ATTRIBUTE).     assertTrue("Age is not readable", attr.isReadable()).     assertFalse("Age is not writable", attr.isWritable()). }

@Test public void testNickNameIsExposed() throws Exception {     ModelMBeanInfo inf = (ModelMBeanInfo) getMBeanInfo().     MBeanAttributeInfo attr = inf.getAttribute("NickName").     assertNotNull("Nick Name should not be null", attr).     assertTrue("Nick Name should be writable", attr.isWritable()).     assertTrue("Nick Name should be readable", attr.isReadable()). }

@Override protected MBeanInfoAssembler getAssembler() throws Exception {     MethodExclusionMBeanInfoAssembler assembler = new MethodExclusionMBeanInfoAssembler().     Properties props = new Properties().     props.setProperty(OBJECT_NAME, "setAge,isSuperman,setSuperman,dontExposeMe").     assembler.setIgnoredMethodMappings(props).     return assembler. }
